Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.49,0:00:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.69,0:00:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.16,0:00:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.70,0:00:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.81,0:00:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.02,0:00:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.82,0:00:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.10,0:01:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.54,0:01:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.21,0:01:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.85,0:01:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.93,0:01:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!打倒傑克斯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.30,0:01:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊!殺死他!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.40,0:01:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!莉莉娜殿下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.67,0:01:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.91,0:01:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的王兄!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.44,0:01:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光榮歸於衛星!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.34,0:01:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十七話\N背叛的遙遠故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.02,0:01:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令部音訊全無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.89,0:01:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們逃出去!快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.89,0:01:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.69,0:01:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.46,0:02:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.18,0:02:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球圈統一聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.05,0:02:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派遣宇宙軍去衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.32,0:02:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚴厲限制衛星居民的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.39,0:02:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合高層崩潰後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.25,0:02:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙軍也留在衛星\N鞏固其支配權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.09,0:02:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在由西伯利亞升空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.73,0:02:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的宇宙攻擊用機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陶拉斯的機動性面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.76,0:02:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們的勢力正不斷減弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.74,0:02:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合的士兵們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.41,0:02:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止無意義的反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.94,0:02:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們OZ來宇宙是為了帶來和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.51,0:02:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，一起迎接新時代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.23,0:03:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陶拉斯MD部隊沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.36,0:03:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該說情況很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.17,0:03:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼\N叫無人陶拉斯回去巴爾吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.84,0:03:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,護衛方面怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.21,0:03:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星的人當機動戰士是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.14,0:03:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日暫時讓我獨自行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.45,0:03:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.12,0:03:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD部隊解除戰鬥\N回去巴爾吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.74,0:03:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD?無人戰鬥兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.34,0:03:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的OZ，開始了兒戲的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.81,0:03:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.41,0:04:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙的居民應該是自由的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.52,0:04:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N地球圈統一聯合壓制你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.69,0:04:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個聯合的時代已經完結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.73,0:04:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球，新的秩序將要建立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.40,0:04:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這個宇宙也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.30,0:04:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是自由的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.03,0:04:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ會支持各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以上是OZ軍\N不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.64,0:04:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是維持和平機關OZ送來的訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.15,0:04:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，我想討論一下這議題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.95,0:04:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ也不急於想要結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.99,0:04:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.99,0:04:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,D區的衛星會議\N今日就到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.97,0:04:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.67,0:04:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，別客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.71,0:04:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我現在以個人身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.54,0:05:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我想所有衛星早晚會感謝OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.24,0:05:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是個很年輕的領袖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.98,0:05:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能不能請你把年輕\N看做事一種可能性呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這種衛星第三世代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.15,0:05:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和不懂區別聯合軍與OZ的老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ也曾是隸屬聯合的組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.63,0:05:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能馬上要衛星的人了解吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舊聯合的部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.77,0:05:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還駐守在各處的衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.30,0:05:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見，我要解放下一個衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.44,0:05:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，還未請教芳名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.41,0:05:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是OZ在宇宙的指揮官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.12,0:05:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.20,0:05:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令駐守在各衛星的\N舊聯合軍勢力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.97,0:06:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相繼投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉著OZ的新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.27,0:06:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,設置在衛星間的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.04,0:06:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙機雷的清除工程也開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.54,0:06:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，各衛星間的交流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也會再次開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ用甚麼手段也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.95,0:06:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們不是要把衛星歸其支配下嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.99,0:06:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，是最醜惡的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被武力強迫屈服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.79,0:06:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還會留有反抗的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.49,0:06:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但若以支援的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星就會認同OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.33,0:06:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為宇宙以輕率的傢伙為主流啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.77,0:06:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們毫無發覺OZ的陰謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.84,0:06:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們應該回去宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.27,0:06:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和鋼彈一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.04,0:06:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈是為了衛星的人\N而造出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.11,0:06:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能從OZ的陰謀裡保護大家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.95,0:06:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但怎樣飛上宇宙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.02,0:06:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們行動不能張揚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們反而要張揚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.99,0:07:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然OZ冒充和平企圖支配衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.36,0:07:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們就不能再以衛星為擋箭牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.77,0:07:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ已經戴上虛假的外表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，衛星的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.14,0:07:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就會知道OZ的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.68,0:07:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的OZ不會認為那是上策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.38,0:07:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是我們又能戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.85,0:07:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們回去宇宙吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.62,0:07:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.93,0:07:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令這一區的聯合軍全部投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.63,0:07:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是為暗殺希‧唯一事贖罪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用那樣說吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說OZ和那件事有關的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.90,0:07:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,始終只是謠言!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.17,0:07:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是OZ說的不同版本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.21,0:07:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長老，你為何會來這裡!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.71,0:07:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我聽聞你們在商量認同OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.02,0:07:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的OZ期望和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.42,0:08:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們不能輕易信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.19,0:08:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前和現在也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.66,0:08:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個蕾蒂‧安特校值得信任!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她以前多次採用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.23,0:08:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,血腥的高壓行動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.73,0:08:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是謠言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她現在不是正親自指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.10,0:08:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,清除宇宙機雷\N這種危險任務嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.84,0:08:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他們想得到宇宙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.34,0:08:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們現在為衛星工作是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.05,0:08:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ想向我們伸出和平之手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不應該拒絕他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和地球友好是我們的基本政策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.69,0:08:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們認同OZ吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.23,0:08:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們只是一群可惡的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在叫MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.63,0:08:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先去宇宙機雷區域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.40,0:08:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙機雷接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.45,0:09:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是尼高爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.65,0:09:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,P0314區工程完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.52,0:09:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打掃宇宙也變得簡單了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.66,0:09:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在衛星D13087
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.77,0:09:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現疑似鋼彈製造工場的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.37,0:09:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及逮捕了一名技術師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上回來司令部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這個男人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.75,0:09:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指揮官終於出場了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍部機械工場的地底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.62,0:09:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有能製造機動戰士的外部區域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.89,0:09:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他把那裡破壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.32,0:09:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毀滅証據嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.23,0:09:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可惜，他也毀滅了資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是你造出鋼彈的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人這樣發問的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.27,0:09:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該和那5部鋼彈有關!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.87,0:10:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和其餘4部無關呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.51,0:10:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我造出最好的鋼彈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.91,0:10:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何須要造出4部不同的鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.58,0:10:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說你造出的只有1部嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.29,0:10:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.66,0:10:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是名為[死神鋼彈]的傑作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是巧合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.86,0:10:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星間的往來和通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.06,0:10:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直被聯合封鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.90,0:10:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是造了1部出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巧合?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.60,0:10:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說有5部是巧合嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.07,0:10:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校!地球有通訊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新加坡宇宙港基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.08,0:10:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正受到鋼彈02和04的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.41,0:10:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.22,0:10:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然要回來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.50,0:10:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是OZ的大型基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣不能前進啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要一口氣衝去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.34,0:11:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動戰士升空用的HLV
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.89,0:11:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾!別勉強!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勉強也好，我要大家知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.03,0:11:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要戰鬥到同伴知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要大家看見我們的戰鬥後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道須要回去宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙在等我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.19,0:11:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要和大家一起去宇宙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.74,0:12:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是鋼彈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.28,0:12:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們正攻擊OZ在地球的基地啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.31,0:12:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合軍的確會迫害衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.08,0:12:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而OZ也會隸屬聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.65,0:12:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何一個衛星向地球投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.36,0:12:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也並非不能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.02,0:12:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，現在正是要OZ重新知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.13,0:12:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們對和平的渴求的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.13,0:12:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不可以永遠拿著武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.00,0:12:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們相信戰鬥有助於保護衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.77,0:12:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不!現在對衛星來說是麻煩!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在OZ不信任我們之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.54,0:12:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們應該表明自己的態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.78,0:12:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為愛\N因為此任何人更愛衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.68,0:12:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們選擇了戰鬥之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.48,0:12:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈…在拼死戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.99,0:13:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們…以些微的力量在反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.83,0:13:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們為何不保護那些鋼彈!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.38,0:13:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.52,0:13:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我們的事全世界都知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.79,0:13:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要發表宇宙衛星D區的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.53,0:13:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今在地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.83,0:13:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名為鋼彈的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.67,0:13:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正進行破壞OZ的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.67,0:13:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們D區和鋼彈毫無關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.91,0:13:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們宣佈若鋼彈當OZ是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.38,0:13:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我們也就成為鋼彈的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.98,0:14:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ光明正大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,互相的誤解已經消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.22,0:14:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們現在希望鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.72,0:14:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這場戰鬥裡被擊倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.46,0:14:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們希望所有區域的衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會認同這宣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.19,0:14:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白!我明白但受不了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.77,0:14:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊，迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.63,0:14:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們本來就是獨自來到地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.64,0:14:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在得不到衛星明白也不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.21,0:14:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有和我一條心並肩作戰的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.81,0:14:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經足夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.12,0:14:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起來!沙漠鋼彈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.77,0:14:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還不可以被擊倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.68,0:15:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.34,0:15:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去會沒命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.55,0:15:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們應該在做正確的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.12,0:15:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何要死在這種地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.49,0:15:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因為我們是正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.03,0:15:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是正義!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.15,0:15:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.65,0:15:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正義的人不強大怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.25,0:15:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若你們到此為止沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.05,0:15:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後的就留給剩下的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.93,0:15:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我把之後的交給你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.66,0:15:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.07,0:15:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若死在這裡，你們會對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.67,0:16:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得贊同你們所想的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.67,0:16:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家注意到了嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.91,0:16:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家…大家知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.63,0:16:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的任務是消滅OZ組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果OZ上了宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.73,0:16:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要追上去消滅他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥會變得艱辛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.71,0:16:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我從五顆心裡感到詳和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.95,0:16:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第五名技術者躲藏的衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.86,0:16:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然其他四名輕易被逮住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.49,0:17:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但始終也會有人頑強反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.03,0:17:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校\N雖然衛星外圍區域有工場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.97,0:17:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但通往內部的通路完全被封閉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.11,0:17:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發出勸降警告了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.11,0:17:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警告被忽視了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.41,0:17:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不用客氣，開始攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.95,0:17:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校!衛星有熱源反應!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.02,0:17:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全體散開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩部有人機被毀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.30,0:17:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD部隊\N因反應速度快沒損毀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.63,0:17:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陶拉斯MD部隊專用雷射炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校!雷射炮太強了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.34,0:17:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直接擊中衛星\N會有很嚴重的損毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.31,0:17:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的戰鬥方式何時起變得有禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.98,0:17:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼哥爾，我現在並非進行外交
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.18,0:17:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我應該正在戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.72,0:18:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星並非被我們的攻擊毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.26,0:18:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它是被叛亂份子所毀滅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.66,0:18:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的精神仍然卑鄙無恥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.23,0:18:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.03,0:18:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我就自動投降吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我接受你的投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.20,0:18:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.47,0:18:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星的人早晚也會發覺到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.98,0:18:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ邪惡的一面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.11,0:18:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會白費這些孩子的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.86,0:18:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點!卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全體包圍鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.43,0:18:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有機動戰士升空用HLV
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.67,0:18:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去，升空時會被圍攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.34,0:18:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾!快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.84,0:18:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管我，我決定了要掩護升空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.98,0:19:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!你說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.82,0:19:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家一定要去宇宙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.72,0:19:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，所以我在這裡掩護大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少你們兩個能去到宇宙
